      "content": "oh wow okay i didn't realize it was that serious. i thought because it was just an herbal supplement it wouldn't mess with the prescription too much. are you sure though? i've read some places online that says it's fine if you just take a small dose at a different time of day. like if i just took it in the morning and the sertraline at night, would that be safer?",
