      "content": "i get what ur saying but i really dont want to wait weeks for a doctor appt while i'm struggling with these exams. is there a specific dose of the st johns wort that is considered safe enough where it wouldn't actually trigger that serotonin thing? like if i just took a tiny bit, would it be okay?",
